sac.graph

Class GraphSearchAlgorithm

  • java.lang.Object
    • sac.SearchAlgorithm
      • sac.graph.GraphSearchAlgorithm
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AStar, BestFirstSearch, BreadthFirstSearch, DepthFirstSearch, Dijkstra, IterativeDeepeningAStar

    public abstract class GraphSearchAlgorithm
extends SearchAlgorithm
    Abstract graph search algorithm. Meant to be extended by actual algorithms e.g.: Breadth First Search, Depth First Search, Dijkstra's, Best First Search, A*, IDA*.
    Author:
    Przemysław Klęsk (wi.zut.edu.pl), Marcin Korzeń (wi.zut.edu.pl)
